Package: nimbleTools
Title: Tools for Running and Diagnosing NIMBLE Models
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Miguel Ángel", "Beltrán-Sánchez", , "angel.beltran@uv.es", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Miguel Ángel", "Martínez-Beneito", , "miguel.a.martinez@uv.es", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides tools for running 'NIMBLE' MCMC chains in parallel, diagnosing problematic MCMC behaviour, and using a Leroux CAR distribution in 'NIMBLE' model code. Optional features include posterior summaries, WAIC calculation, and HMC sampling.
